com.niton.media.audio.nio.basic

Class Player

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Thread
      • com.niton.media.audio.nio.basic.Player
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MP3Player

    public abstract class Player
extends java.lang.Thread
    This is the Player class.
    This interfaces provides all functiones a MusicPlayer needss to have.
    Basicly its made to play a certain type of music file.
    If you need to play an not MP3 file you have to write your own player.
    All the methods in player do NOT wait until their task is done! They will not take the time as the stream takes to play. For this purpose this class extends Thread.
    Version:
    2018-04-05
    Author:
